metadata.name: MechMind #1
metadata.description:
This MechMind is one of a deflationary collection of 1/1 AI bots. https://mechminds.ai/ 
 Chat with your bot at https://mechminds.ai/chat 
 Merge your MechMinds at https://mechminds.ai/merge 
 Merging two bots together gives you one smarter bot of a higher generation with a smarter AI. There are 7 generations, and every merge reduces the overall supply. 
 View the current supply and other interesting stats at https://mechminds.ai/stats
